Merb.thor now lives in merb-gen, so you can easily regenerate it through 
'merb-gen app .' - here's a shortcut: http://merbivore.com/merb.thor

To stay on the edge of merb.thor development you can fetch it like this:

curl -L http://merbivore.com/merb.thor > merb.thor

Visit http://merbunity.com/tutorials/18 for more information.
